WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:14.524
Managing Secrets

00:00:14.524 --> 00:00:31.810
The trap: .env in the repo

00:00:31.810 --> 00:00:53.803
Step 1: Set an env-mode secret

00:00:53.803 --> 00:01:19.904
Step 2: Set a file-mode secret

00:01:19.904 --> 00:01:37.151
Step 3: List what you have

00:01:37.151 --> 00:01:51.233
You can never read it back

00:01:51.233 --> 00:02:14.683
Step 4: Get returns a digest

00:02:14.683 --> 00:02:37.988
Step 5: Rotate when you forget

00:02:37.988 --> 00:02:58.690
Step 6: Deploy with both secrets

00:02:58.690 --> 00:03:15.619
Step 7: The env secret arrives

00:03:15.619 --> 00:03:38.222
Step 8: The file secret arrives

00:03:38.222 --> 00:03:55.763
The fork punchline

00:03:55.763 --> 00:04:12.411
Step 9: Fork the repo

00:04:12.411 --> 00:04:33.823
Step 10: The fork lists empty

00:04:33.823 --> 00:04:57.256
Step 11: The fork cannot start

00:04:57.256 --> 00:05:02.376
Next: Backup & Restore
